Bus tracker that will auto update the bus position every 15sec on its route from MIT campus in Cambridge to the Harvard campus, also in Cambridge. 

To start, simply press the "Show stops between MIT and Harvard", the marker will auto-update every 15seconds with the new position of the bus.

Current changes that have been made include: Increased map brightness, changed font size on start button and decreased opacity on button box.

Future changes could include updated bus marker, map style changes and rearranged start button.

All licensing information can be found in the LICENSE file.
